{"tid":1996514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秘密狗賊於秘密狗車車內向途人大叫黑記，引來傳媒爭相拍攝","createTime":"2020-05-01T04:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T06:54:20.000Z","uid":51271,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82ca0e64db5864ff409c50efdb4a8b6353d8958a","tid":1996514,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102900447812025/videos/303525157300517/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102900447812025%2Fvideos%2F303525157300517%2F&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=57fa363e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102900447812025/videos/303525157300517/</a><br />\n<br />\n【便衣警員侮辱記者市民女警情緒激動】<br />\n<br />\n有便衣警員乘私家車，車牌VC6174，於洗衣街向途經的市民及記者大叫「曱甴」及「黑記」，引來傳媒爭相拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n一名女警登上私家車後繼續挑釁一位女記者，女警其後更拉低車窗破口大罵。<br />\n<br />\n一輛車牌為UT9246的警方私家車亦緊跟其後一同駛去。一班記者隨後包圍該警用私家車，質疑警方為何侮辱記者專業，惟車內警員未有答覆。<br />\n<br />\n特約外勤記者：M、AL、I<br />\n責任編輯：MT<br />\n總編輯檢視：V<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n《黑白新聞RightNews》現已開啟streamlabs贊助功能<br />\n本媒體屬於非牟利傳媒，營運上非常艱辛，非常需要追求新聞真相的朋友幫忙，所有贊助資金將會用於日後營運、外勤人員防護裝備、攝影器材升級。<br />\n贊助網址： <a href=\"https://streamlabs.com/rightnewshk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamlabs.com%2Frightnewshk&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=da30f9f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamlabs.com/rightnewshk</a>"},{"pid":"9184309349b8ac586babd9b43d985f02b0cd0c71","tid":1996514,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0c6812a480d02173c966efd8f7ba736a2469f3","tid":1996514,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"